headline: Has Vulcan Materials Run Too Far After Another 14% YTD Rally in 2025?
summary: Thinking About Vulcan Materials Stock? Here's What You Need to Know First If you are looking at your portfolio and wondering whether Vulcan Materials deserves a place in it, you are definitely not alone. Over the past year, this construction materials giant has been steadily climbing, with the stock notching an impressive 15.6% total return. Looking even further back, the stock is up well over 70% in just three years and nearly 150% in five. This is exactly the kind of historical performance...
